title: Static Analysis

android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD.description: Allows an application to disable the key lock and any associated password security. A legitimate example of this is the phone disabling the key lock when receiving an incoming phone call, then re-enabling the key lock when the call is finished.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS.description: Allows an application to modify the system's settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system's configuration.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.FLASHLIGHT.description: Allows the application to control the flashlight.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.Manifest.permission.READ_PHONE_S.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.WRITE_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to modify the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to erase or modify your contact data.

android.permission.READ_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.flashalerts3.oncallsmsforall.View.PopupActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.

"tip_1" : "

"tip_2" : "

វាពិតជាមានប្រយោជន៍ណាស់សន្សំសំចៃថ្មកាន់តែច្រើនហើយអ្នកនឹងមិនខកខានការហៅឬសារណាមួយឡើយនៅពេលទូរស័ព្ទស្ថិតក្នុងសភាពស្ងាត់។ 

រួមជាមួយមុខងារកម្មវិធីកំណត់ពេលវេលាអ្នកនឹងមានកម្មវិធីល្អឥតខ្ចោះ។"
"text_speak" : "បង្កើតសំឡេងរោទ៍ពីអត្ថបទ"
"text_title_type_flash" : "ជ្រើសរើសប្រភេទពន្លឺភ្លា"

"tip" : "សម្រាប់ទូរស័ព្ទ Android មួយចំនួន, ដើម្បីឱ្យ Flash(ភ្លា) មានស្ថេរភាពការងារអ្នកត្រូវអនុញ្ញាតឱ្យកម្មវិធីនេះដំណើរការនៅផ្ទៃខាងក្រោយជានិច្ច។ ដោយដកកម្មវិធីនេះចេញពីបញ្ជីកំហិតនៃមុខងារសន្សំថាមពលនៅលើទូរស័ព្ទ។"

"tip_1" : "

• ការណែនាំទូទៅ : 
- ការកំណត់ទូរស័ព្ទ> អាគុយ> កម្មវិធីសន្សំសំចៃថ្ម (ឬការពារថ្ម)> Flash 3> ជ្រើសរើសបិទឬមិនដាក់កម្រិត។ 
- ឬ៖ ការកំណត់ទូរស័ព្ទ > គ្រប់គ្រងកម្មវិធី > Flash 3 > ការការពារថ្ម > អនុញ្ញាតឱ្យដំណើរការផ្ទៃខាងក្រោយ"

"tip_2" : "

• ការណែនាំសម្រាប់ទូរស័ព្ទ Huawei៖ 
- ចូលទៅកាន់: ការកំណត់ទូរស័ព្ទ > អាគុយ > បើកដំណើរការកម្មវិធី > Flash 3 > បិទ > យល់ព្រម 
- ឬ: ការកំណត់ទូរស័ព្ទ > អាគុយ > កម្មវិធីដែលត្រូវបានការពារ > Flash 3 > បិទ > យល់ព្រម"

"text_button_tips3" : ". Jika Anda ingin menghemat lebih banyak daya baterai untuk ponsel Anda, Anda harus mengaktifkan fungsi pemberitahuan Flash hanya ketika telepon diatur ke mode getar / Senyap. 

Ini akan sangat berguna, menghemat lebih banyak baterai, dan Anda tidak akan melewatkan panggilan atau pesan apa pun, ketika ponsel dalam mode hening. 

Dikombinasikan dengan fungsi timer, Anda akan memiliki aplikasi yang sempurna."

"tip" : "Untuk beberapa ponsel Android, untuk membuat Flash bekerja secara stabil, Anda harus mengizinkan aplikasi ini untuk selalu berjalan di latar belakang. Dengan menghapus aplikasi ini dari daftar terbatas fitur hemat daya di ponsel."

- Atau: Pengaturan telepon > Kelola aplikasi > Flash 3 > Perlindungan baterai > Biarkan latar belakang berjalan."

"text_button_tips3" : ". यदि आप अपने फोन के लिए अधिक बैटरी पावर बचाना चाहते हैं, आपको फ़्लैश अधिसूचना फ़ंक्शन को केवल तभी चालू करना चाहिए जब फोन वाइब्रेट / साइलेंट मोड पर सेट हो.

"tip" : "कुछ एंड्रॉइड फोन के लिए, फ्लैश के लिए स्थिरता काम करने के लिए, आपको इस एप्लिकेशन को हमेशा पृष्ठभूमि में चलाने की अनुमति देने की आवश्यकता है। इस एप्लिकेशन को फोन पर बिजली की बचत सुविधाओं की प्रतिबंधित सूची से हटा दें।"

- या: फ़ोन सेटिंग > एप्लिकेशन प्रबंधित करें > फ़्लैश 3 > बैटरी सुरक्षा > पृष्ठभूमि चलाने की अनुमति दें."

playstore_details.title: Flash blink on Call, all messages & notifications
playstore_details.description:
Flash 3 (New) is the application to blinks the Flash when you receive a call or message, notification from the apps. Easy to use just one touch ON/OFF. Along with 2 types of flashes for you choose, add many new unique features will definitely make you enjoy and become more different.

Flash 3 is one of the top useful applications that should be available on Android phones. When an incoming call or message arrives (SMS, Facebook Messenger, Whatsapp, Twitter ...), the Flash of the phone will blinks to signal.

👍 The main functions of the application:
✔ Flash blink when a incoming call (Flash alerts on Call)
✔ Flash blink when a Message arrives
✔ Flash notification App: Flash blink when notification from All the apps (when there are messages, calls). 
✔ DJ lights flash for party use
✔ SOS flash: use in important cases, need to create attention around.

👍 Other useful customizations on Flash 3:
✔ Select the blinks style: the application supports 2 different flashing styles that can help you be different.
✔ Change flashing speed (10 different Flashing speeds available)
✔ Smart feature - doesn't flash when you are using the phone
✔ Support both flash front and rear
✔ App compatible with most types of Android phones including all types like Samsung, Oppo, Xiaomi, HTC, Vivo...

Best if you are having party and you can use it as LED lights or DJ lights. In this application you can control the intensity of Flash 3.
It will give you flash light alerts which is very useful at times.


📮 Contact us
Please contact the email below if you have any suggestions or feedback:
flash3software@gmail.com
